{"tid":730051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  48歲李嘉欣懷第2胎","createTime":"2018-07-05T05:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T00:09:53.000Z","uid":48905,"like":46,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"856645aa119cef48edb3c33eba64ec79906bb8dc","tid":730051,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣上月20日渡過48歲生日，她曬出與許晉亨的恩愛照放閃，凍齡樣令人驚艷。30日她又在微博分享聚會照，卻有眼尖網友發現，李嘉欣身形似乎圓潤不少，引發懷孕揣測。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣是中葡混血兒，1988年參加香港小姐競選，獲冠軍，因而有「最美港姐」封號。李嘉欣日前在微博分享與閨密聚會照，其中她被老公許晉亨從後方環抱，甜蜜模樣令人稱羨。 已有1子的李嘉欣身型明顯變圓潤，許多人猜測，李嘉欣又懷有身孕，紛紛留言，「又有寶寶了嗎？」、「看著像是懷孕啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133618_96e52e185e322f6394bb15090d0bb76d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133618_96e52e185e322f6394bb15090d0bb76d.png&h=89b37f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133622_01acd533ce0b7b719120deb1ba00757d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133622_01acd533ce0b7b719120deb1ba00757d.png&h=e76279b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5beb797a71db6febe2eb7912ca7680053830c067","tid":730051,"uid":48905,"like":152,"dislike":3,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ee742424b5150dddaee9f08dc00fd22f7c35d9","tid":730051,"uid":44243,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"咪撚癲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e30b14a20ae32faa86ef59c7eb3ea49834e4653","tid":730051,"uid":132587,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"cite